1. install react app starter with typescript:
npx create-react-app resux-ts --template typescript

2. install following packages:
npm install --save-exact @types/react-redux@7.1.15 axios@0.21.1 react-redux@7.2.2 redux@4.0.5 redux-thunk@2.3.0

3. Create the reducer to handle various action types. state/reducers

4. Create action-creaors to dispatch the action. state/action-creators